      "reason": "Decomposed src/scistudio/api/routes/ai_pty.py (757 LOC) into a sub-package with __init__.py owning router + monkeypatch-seam state + _spawn, plus engine.py, websocket.py, validation.py, subscribers.py, internal_routes.py. Submodules use late-bound _pkg.<name> lookups so existing monkeypatch contracts on the package survive. Added 41 tests under tests/api/routes/ai_pty/ (public surface + per-submodule behaviour). Removed ai_pty.py from GOD_FILE_SIZE_WAIVERS. Updated ADR-034 / ADR-035 frontmatter governance to reference the new package path + the submodule-qualified open_engine_initiated_tab contract. All 31 pre-existing ai_pty tests + 41 new tests pass; full_audit pass; sentrux pass."
    }
